1. **WORKFLOW 0 - Understand Project**: First, I must understand the project structure and context before doing anything.
2. **WORKFLOW 1 - Read progress.txt**: Identify the most important pending task. Tasks are prioritized by `[P<number>]` tags — `[P0]` is highest priority, `[P1000+]` is low priority (doable when possible, not ignorable; revert if taking too long).
